161
00:07:49,861 --> 00:07:51,129
Oh, my God.

162
00:07:51,297 --> 00:07:53,302
Determine if the patient
is a candidate for...

163
00:07:53,386 --> 00:07:55,606
All right,
we can save your life, Canaan,

164
00:07:55,691 --> 00:07:57,871
but the operation
is going to require

165
00:07:57,956 --> 00:08:00,067
