You always mind the rules,
Floyd.

197
00:09:35,938 --> 00:09:37,551
Good kid.

198
00:09:38,083 --> 00:09:40,087
Never too late to fix that.

199
00:09:43,018 --> 00:09:44,806
Oh, come on, now.

200
